<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Simulador Tributário - Grupo Maradel</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        /* TEMA ESCURO PROFUNDO */
        :root { 
            --laranja: #DB8438; 
            --bg-fundo: #09090b; 
            --bg-painel: #18181b; 
            --borda: #27272a; 
            --texto-claro: #f4f4f5; 
            --texto-medio: #a1a1aa;
            --bg-input: #121214;
        }
        body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg-fundo); color: var(--texto-claro); overflow: hidden; }
        
        .text-maradel { color: var(--laranja); font-weight: bold; }
        .btn-maradel { background-color: var(--laranja); color: white; font-weight: bold; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn-maradel:hover { background-color: #b86b2a; }
        
        table.sim-table { table-layout: fixed; width: max-content; min-width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; }
        .sim-table th { font-size: 12px; background-color: #111113; color: var(--texto-medio); padding: 10px 6px !important; text-transform: uppercase; border-right: 1px solid var(--borda); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borda); }
        .sim-table td { padding: 6px !important; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borda); border-right: 1px solid var(--borda); vertical-align: middle; }
        
        input[type="text"], input[type="password"] { font-size: 15px !important; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; border: 1px solid var(--borda); background-color: var(--bg-input); color: white; border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 4px; width: 100%; outline-color: var(--laranja); transition: 0.2s; }
        input[type="password"] { text-align: left; }
        input[type="text"]:focus, input[type="password"]:focus { border-color: var(--laranja); box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(219, 132, 56, 0.3); }
        textarea { border: 1px solid var(--borda); border-radius: 4px; padding: 12px; width: 100%; background: var(--bg-input); color: white; outline-color: var(--laranja); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre; }
        
        .tab-active { border-bottom: 3px solid var(--laranja); font-weight: bold; color: var(--laranja); }
        .plus-btn { background: var(--laranja); color: white; border-radius: 50%; width: 24px; height: 24px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; border: none; }
        
        .ref-table th { background-color: #111113; color: var(--texto-medio); font-size: 13px; padding: 10px 6px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid var(--borda); }
        .ref-table td { background-color: var(--bg-painel); color: var(--texto-claro); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid var(--borda); padding: 8px 4px; }
        .ref-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background-color: #27272a; }
        
        .custom-checkbox input:not(:checked) + div { background-color: transparent; color: transparent; border-color: #52525b; }
        .custom-checkbox input:checked + div { background-color: var(--laranja); border-color: var(--laranja); color: white; }
        
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; height: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg-fundo); border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #3f3f46; border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: var(--laranja); }

        .bg-painel { background-color: var(--bg-painel); }
        .border-painel { border-color: var(--borda); }
        .text-dim { color: var(--texto-medio); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="w-full h-screen flex flex-col">

    <!-- Modais de Controle (Remoção, Aplicação e Reset) -->
    <div id="modalConfirm" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 z-50 flex items-center justify-center backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="bg-[#1e1e20] p-6 rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-md border border-[#333336]">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-3 text-red-400">Atenção!</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 text-sm" id="modalText"></p>
            <div class="flex justify-end gap-3">
                <button onclick="fecharModal()" class="px-5 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-gray-300 bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600">Cancelar</button>
                <button onclick="confirmarRemocaoAnexo()" class="px-5 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-white bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700">Sim, Remover</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modalConfirmAplicar" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 z-50 flex items-center justify-center backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="bg-[#1e1e20] p-6 rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-md border border-[#333336]">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-3 text-maradel">Aplicar Valores</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 text-sm">Deseja aplicar os valores deste mês para os meses seguintes? Isso substituirá os dados já digitados.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-end gap-3">
                <button onclick="fecharModalAplicar()" class="px-5 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-gray-300 bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600">Não</button>
                <button onclick="confirmarAplicarParaBaixo()" class="px-5 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-white btn-maradel">Sim, Aplicar</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modalReset" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 z-50 flex items-center justify-center backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="bg-[#1e1e20] p-6 rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-md border border-[#333336] text-center">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-2 text-white">Nova Consulta</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6 text-sm">Tem certeza que deseja limpar tudo? O simulador será redefinido ao estado inicial.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
                <button onclick="document.getElementById('modalReset').classList.add('hidden')" class="px-5 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-gray-300 bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600">Cancelar</button>
                <button onclick="location.reload()" class="px-5 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-white bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700">Limpar Tudo</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Modal Anexo Personalizado -->
    <div id="modalPers" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 z-[70] flex items-center justify-center backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="bg-[#1e1e20] p-6 rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-sm border border-[#333336]">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-2 text-maradel" id="modalPersTitle">Configurar Abatimentos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6 text-xs">Selecione os impostos que serão <b>ABATIDOS (ISENTOS)</b> neste anexo personalizado.</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-6" id="listaImpostosPers">
                <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" id="pers_IRPJ" class="w-4 h-4 accent-maradel"><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-300">IRPJ</span></label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" id="pers_CSLL" class="w-4 h-4 accent-maradel"><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-300">CSLL</span></label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" id="pers_Cofins" class="w-4 h-4 accent-maradel"><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-300">COFINS</span></label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" id="pers_Pis" class="w-4 h-4 accent-maradel"><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-300">PIS</span></label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" id="pers_CPP" class="w-4 h-4 accent-maradel"><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-300">CPP / INSS</span></label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" id="pers_ICMS" class="w-4 h-4 accent-maradel"><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-300">ICMS</span></label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" id="pers_ISS" class="w-4 h-4 accent-maradel"><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-300">ISS</span></label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" id="pers_IPI" class="w-4 h-4 accent-maradel"><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-300">IPI</span></label>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-end gap-3">
                <button onclick="fecharConfigPers()" class="px-5 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-gray-300 bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600">Cancelar</button>
                <button onclick="salvarConfigPers()" class="px-5 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-white bg-maradel hover:bg-orange-600">Salvar Padrão</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Modal Senha e Configuração Geral -->
    <div id="modalSenha" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 z-50 flex items-center justify-center backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="bg-[#1e1e20] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-2xl border border-[#333336] w-full max-w-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-2 text-white">Acesso Restrito</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mb-5">Insira a senha de administrador para alterar as alíquotas oficiais.</p>
            <input type="password" id="senhaAdmin" placeholder="Digite a senha..." class="mb-2" onkeypress="if(event.key === 'Enter') verificarSenha()">
            <div id="erroSenha" class="text-red-400 text-xs font-bold hidden mb-2">Senha incorreta.</div>
            <div id="dicaSenha" class="text-blue-300 text-xs font-bold hidden mb-4 bg-[#121c2a] p-2 rounded border border-[#1e2a3a]">Dica: O seu próprio nome, com a primeira letra maiúscula.</div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-5">
                <button onclick="mostrarDica()" class="text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 underline">Esqueci a senha</button>
                <div class="flex gap-2">
                    <button onclick="fecharModalSenha()" class="px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-gray-300 bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600">Cancelar</button>
                    <button onclick="verificarSenha()" class="px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-white bg-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-500">Acessar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Modal Configurações JSON -->
    <div id="modalConfig" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-black/90 z-[60] flex items-center justify-center backdrop-blur-sm p-4">
        <div class="bg-[#1e1e20] p-6 rounded-xl shadow-2xl border border-[#333336] w-full max-w-5xl h-[85vh] flex flex-col">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">Módulo de Configurações - Tabelas Referenciais</h3>
                    <p class="text-red-400 text-xs font-bold">CUIDADO: Erros de formatação neste painel quebram o simulador.</p>
                </div>
                <button onclick="fecharModalConfig()" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-white font-bold text-2xl">&times;</button>
            </div>
            <textarea id="jsonEditor" class="flex-grow bg-[#09090b] text-green-400 border-[#333336] p-4 mb-4 font-mono text-sm"></textarea>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                <button onclick="restaurarTabelasPadrao()" class="px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-gray-300 bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600">↻ Restaurar Lei 2026</button>
                <div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
                    <span id="msgSalvar" class="text-green-400 font-bold text-xs hidden">✔ Salvo! Atualizando...</span>
                    <span id="msgErroSalvar" class="text-red-400 font-bold text-xs hidden">❌ JSON Inválido.</span>
                    <button onclick="salvarTabelasEditadas()" class="px-6 py-2 rounded text-sm font-bold text-white bg-green-700 hover:bg-green-600">💾 Salvar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CABEÇALHO SUPER COMPACTO -->
    <div class="w-full px-4 pt-4 pb-2 border-b border-[#27272a] bg-[#09090b] shrink-0">
        <header class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white leading-none">GRUPO <span class="text-maradel">MARADEL</span></h1>
                <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-dim tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mt-1">Consultoria Contábil & Estratégica</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 no-print items-center">
                <button onclick="document.getElementById('modalReset').classList.remove('hidden')" class="px-4 py-2 rounded shadow text-white bg-[#27272a] border border-[#3f3f46] hover:bg-[#3f3f46] font-bold text-xs flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors">
                    🔄 Nova Consulta
                </button>
                <button onclick="abrirModalSenha()" class="px-4 py-2 rounded shadow text-white bg-[#27272a] border border-[#3f3f46] hover:bg-[#3f3f46] font-bold text-xs flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors">
                    ⚙️ Config.
                </button>
                <div class="relative group">
                    <button class="btn-maradel px-6 py-2 rounded shadow-lg flex items-center gap-2 text-xs uppercase">Relatórios ▼</button>
                    <!-- Ponte invisível estendida para o hover não sumir -->
                    <div class="absolute hidden group-hover:block right-0 top-full pt-1 pb-2 w-48 z-50">
                        <div class="bg-painel border border-[#3f3f46] rounded shadow-xl text-xs overflow-hidden mt-1">
                            <button onclick="window.print()" class="w-full text-left p-3 hover:bg-[#27272a] border-b border-[#333336] font-bold text-white">📄 Exportar PDF</button>
                            <button onclick="exportarExcel()" class="w-full text-left p-3 hover:bg-[#27272a] font-bold text-white">📊 Gerar Excel XLSX</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <nav class="flex gap-8 no-print pt-2">
            <button onclick="aba('sim')" id="aSim" class="pb-2 text-sm tab-active uppercase tracking-wide">Simulador Estratégico</button>
            <button onclick="aba('ref')" id="aRef" class="pb-2 text-sm text-dim font-bold uppercase hover:text-white transition-colors tracking-wide">Tabelas de Lei</button>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <!-- ÁREA PRINCIPAL FLEXÍVEL -->
    <div class="flex-grow flex flex-col p-4 overflow-hidden">
        
        <div id="cSim" class="flex flex-col h-full">
            <!-- PAINEL DE CONTROLE COMPACTO EM LINHA (5 COLUNAS) -->
            <div class="bg-painel p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-painel mb-4 flex gap-6 shrink-0 no-print items-start">
                
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                    <div class="w-32">
                        <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-dim mb-1 block uppercase">Abertura</label>
                        <input type="text" id="dataAb" oninput="mascaraData(this)" onblur="preencherEIniciar()" placeholder="MM/AAAA" class="!text-left !text-sm p-2 transition-colors duration-500" maxlength="7">
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-32">
                        <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-maradel mb-1 block uppercase">Início Sim.</label>
                        <input type="text" id="dataSim" oninput="mascaraData(this)" onblur="iniciarSimulador()" placeholder="MM/AAAA" class="!text-left !text-sm p-2 !bg-[#2a1c12] !border-[#DB8438]" maxlength="7">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="w-px bg-[#333336] mx-2 self-stretch"></div>

                <!-- 5 COLUNAS DE ANEXOS COM OPÇÃO PERSONALIZADA -->
                <div class="flex-grow grid grid-cols-5 gap-4">
                    
                    <!-- Coluna Anexo I -->
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                        <span class="text-[11px] font-black text-maradel border-b border-[#333336] pb-1 uppercase flex items-center justify-between">ANEXO I</span>
                        
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between group/tt relative w-full">
                            <label class="custom-checkbox flex items-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer">
                                <input type="checkbox" class="hidden" id="chkAnexo1" value="1" onchange="tentarToggleAnexo('1')">
                                <div class="w-3.5 h-3.5 border rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] font-bold">✔</div>
                                <span class="font-bold text-[10px] text-gray-300">Normal (5102)</span>
                            </label>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-black text-white border border-gray-600 text-[9px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center cursor-help shrink-0">!</div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-full right-0 mb-1 w-48 p-2 bg-black border border-gray-700 text-white text-[10px] font-normal rounded hidden group-hover/tt:block z-[60] shadow-xl pointer-events-none normal-case">
                                Venda de mercadorias sem substituição tributária.
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between group/tt relative w-full">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-wrap leading-none">
                                <label class="custom-checkbox flex items-center gap-1 cursor-pointer">
                                    <input type="checkbox" class="hidden" id="chkAnexo1_ST" value="1_ST" onchange="tentarToggleAnexo('1_ST')">
                                    <div class="w-3 h-3 border rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-bold">✔</div>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-[10px] text-gray-300 tracking-tight">ST ICMS (5405)</span>
                                </label>
                                <label class="custom-checkbox flex items-center gap-0.5 cursor-pointer ml-0.5" title="Isentar também PIS e COFINS (Monofásico)">
                                    <input type="checkbox" class="hidden" id="chkAnexo1_ST_Mono" onchange="recalc()">
                                    <div class="w-3 h-3 border rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-bold">✔</div>
                                    <span class="font-normal text-[9px] text-maradel whitespace-nowrap">+ Mono</span>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-black text-white border border-gray-600 text-[9px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center cursor-help shrink-0">!</div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-full right-0 mb-1 w-48 p-2 bg-black border border-gray-700 text-white text-[10px] font-normal rounded hidden group-hover/tt:block z-[60] shadow-xl pointer-events-none normal-case">
                                Mercadorias com ICMS retido por ST. Marque '+ Mono' para isentar também PIS e COFINS.
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between group/tt relative w-full">
                            <label class="custom-checkbox flex items-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer">
                                <input type="checkbox" class="hidden" id="chkAnexo1_EXP" value="1_EXP" onchange="tentarToggleAnexo('1_EXP')">
                                <div class="w-3.5 h-3.5 border rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] font-bold">✔</div>
                                <span class="font-bold text-[10px] text-gray-300">Exportação</span>
                            </label>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-black text-white border border-gray-600 text-[9px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center cursor-help shrink-0">!</div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-full right-0 mb-1 w-48 p-2 bg-black border border-gray-700 text-white text-[10px] font-normal rounded hidden group-hover/tt:block z-[60] shadow-xl pointer-events-none normal-case">
                                Venda para mercado externo (Isento ICMS, PIS, COFINS).
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between group/tt relative w-full">
                            <label class="custom-checkbox flex items-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer">
                                <input type="checkbox" class="hidden" id="chkAnexo1_PERS" value="1_PERS" onchange="tentarToggleAnexo('1_PERS')">
                                <div class="w-3.5 h-3.5 border rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] font-bold">✔</div>
                                <span class="font-bold text-[10px] text-gray-300 flex items-center gap-1">
                                    Personalizado <button onclick="event.preventDefault(); event.stopPropagation(); abrirConfigPers('1_PERS')" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-maradel ml-1" title="Configurar Impostos a Abater">⚙️</button>
                                </span>
                            </label>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-black text-white border border-gray-600 text-[9px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center cursor-help shrink-0">!</div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-full right-0 mb-1 w-48 p-2 bg-black border border-gray-700 text-white text-[10px] font-normal rounded hidden group-hover/tt:block z-[60] shadow-xl pointer-events-none normal-case">
                                Configuração manual de abatimentos isentos ou retidos.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Coluna Anexo II -->
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                        <span class="text-[11px] font-black text-maradel border-b border-[#333336] pb-1 uppercase flex items-center justify-between">ANEXO II</span>
                        
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between group/tt relative w-full">
                            <label class="custom-checkbox flex items-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer">
                                <input type="checkbox" class="hidden" id="chkAnexo2" value="2" onchange="tentarToggleAnexo('2')">
                                <div class="w-3.5 h-3.5 border rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] font-bold">✔</div>
                                <span class="font-bold text-[10px] text-gray-300">Normal (5101)</span>
                            </label>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-black text-white border border-gray-600 text-[9px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center cursor-help shrink-0">!</div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-full right-0 mb-1 w-48 p-2 bg-black border border-gray-700 text-white text-[10px] font-normal rounded hidden group-hover/tt:block z-[60] shadow-xl pointer-events-none normal-case">
                                Venda de produtos industrializados.
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between group/tt relative w-full">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-wrap leading-none">
                                <label class="custom-checkbox flex items-center gap-1 cursor-pointer">
                                    <input type="checkbox" class="hidden" id="chkAnexo2_ST" value="2_ST" onchange="tentarToggleAnexo('2_ST')">
                                    <div class="w-3 h-3 border rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-bold">✔</div>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-[10px] text-gray-300 tracking-tight">ST ICMS/IPI (5401)</span>
                                </label>
                                <label class="custom-checkbox flex items-center gap-0.5 cursor-pointer ml-0.5" title="Isentar também PIS e COFINS (Monofásico)">
                                    <input type="checkbox" class="hidden" id="chkAnexo2_ST_Mono" onchange="recalc()">
                                    <div class="w-3 h-3 border rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-bold">✔</div>
                                    <span class="font-normal text-[9px] text-maradel whitespace-nowrap">+ Mono</span>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-black text-white border border-gray-600 text-[9px] font-bold flex items-center justify-center cursor-help shrink-0">!</div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-full right-0 mb-1 w-48 p-2 bg-black border border-gray-700 text-white text-[10px] font-normal rounded hidden group-hover/tt:block z-[60] shadow-xl pointer-events-none normal-case">
                                Produtos industrializados com retenção de ICMS/IPI. Marque '+ Mono' para isentar PIS e COFINS.
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between group/tt relative w-full">
